text: Input/Output Data The Input/Output data is the type of data an agent expects and delivers. The SAP CC Notification agent collects notifications from SAP CC instances and emits notification UDRs of the sapcc type. The SAP CC Notification agent emits the following notification UDRs: NotificationUDR For further information, see SAP CC UDRs . MIM For information about the MIM and a list of the general MIM pa rameter s, see Administration and Management in Legacy Desktop . Publishes The agent does not publish any MIM resources. Accesses The agent does not access any MIM resources.
